         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>In the Jovian year Piṅkaḷa, month of Āvaṇi, 15th day, Tuesday, Amuṟta (i.e. Amṛta) veḷai, the Vetāntam of Taṇṭavarāyaṉ was fully copied in Ceṉṉapaṭṭaṉam.</p>
         </div>
